{"tid":2154162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想分享比各位知道澳門嘅健康碼點運作","createTime":"2020-08-13T03:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:57:54.000Z","uid":145868,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b21f00c6e3a7a96c8dd0ef15747f0d5d960836","tid":2154162,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"我見香港政府係咁話用健康碼，但又唔公佈任何細節，咁我就分享下澳門健康碼邊到需要scan同需要申報咩資料啦！<br />\n<br />\n首先澳門政府需要所有人進出政府各局門同賭場都要scan健康碼先比你進入，其他食肆同商鋪就唔洗。<br />\n<br />\n咁每次進入以上嘅地方，你都需要scan個qr code, scan完後你就需要填個人資料同埋身份證號碼，之後就有大約4-5個選項問題，大致上問你有冇病症，14日內有冇出境之類問題！<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得除左方便check住人去過邊其他都作用不大，d問題全部都係自己填，而我相信100%嘅人所有問題都會填冇，而check健康碼嘅人都係show一show你有冇填，完全係唔會真係每項對！希望幫到大家"},{"pid":"fe39f619780acaeb0e7dabd890d04475105cf09f","tid":2154162,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f77b0bfeae3c26914ac4530029eaa60bf46cad35","tid":2154162,"uid":280058,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"呢個只係無反抗能力既澳門人既做法<br />\n香港人既健康碼點只咁簡單<br />\n背後既政治目的大到你唔信<br />\n做/ 唔做 已經分到你信唔信呢個政府"},{"pid":"46fadeb34691381d80354c152f6cdd1ea3858ae6","tid":2154162,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"有無得破解？<br />\n偷人身份用得唔得？"},{"pid":"a331f132869798e0c1339449c03389ca9bca29ae","tid":2154162,"uid":213631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dc3532ca882d8a8d6a81e05bf7737b6cfcffca","tid":2154162,"uid":145868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f77b0bfeae3c